<br>
My suggestions for equipment you can get with help:<br>
1) Topmost on your list would probably be a Runed Circlet, should NOT be hard for you with a group of 5 others, go to Permafrost and get the Preacher. This is an EASY camp if you have a cleric and a warrior with you. Any other classes are great at this point, this is a good xp run for the low=mid 20's.<br>
2) Back item also is for you in Perma, the Mammoth cloak. find the alchemist, a slightly harder camp but well worth it.<br>
3) Silver Ruby Veil. See if someone can make you one, the prices are pretty low on those, and if you know an enchanter, you'll do well with this. I had one till my low 40's.<br>
4) wrist: go back and kill evil eyes in the gorge! it WILL pay off for you so you can get another PBB.<br>
<br>
Out of those three things i think an enchanter MIGHT be able to make a veil for you at 100pp but don't quote me on it i'm not sure what gem prices are.<br>
<br>
